304
00:20:03,840 --> 00:20:04,650
Qin Yuebai,

305
00:20:05,650 --> 00:20:07,360
you've really impressed me.

306
00:20:08,170 --> 00:20:09,450
Now that you're here,

307
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:10,970
why don't you have a look around?

308
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:22,930
