329
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:31,080
A businesswoman who trades art

330
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:32,690
was born colorblind.

331
00:21:33,010 --> 00:21:34,600
If everyone knows this...

332
00:21:36,840 --> 00:21:38,450
I understand why you don't want

333
00:21:39,450 --> 00:21:40,600
to keep me by your side.

334
00:22:04,600 --> 00:22:05,840
I did a good job, didn't I?

335
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:07,040
Just you wait.

336
00:22:07,040 --> 00:22:09,080
She'll definitely get what's coming
