337
00:22:09,080 --> 00:22:09,920
How dare she be smug?

338
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:10,720
You're the best.

339
00:22:10,760 --> 00:22:12,520
Ms. Qin, please answer my question.

340
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:14,320
How can you manage the gallery?

341
00:22:15,450 --> 00:22:16,250
Yes.

342
00:22:21,170 --> 00:22:22,760
It's true.

343
00:22:22,760 --> 00:22:24,600
I am indeed
a red-green color-blind patient.

344
00:22:27,690 --> 00:22:28,520
Anyway,

345
00:22:29,080 --> 00:22:30,730
color-blindness
is a congenital condition.

346
00:22:30,840 --> 00:22:32,170
It cannot be chosen.

347
00:22:33,360 --> 00:22:34,520
Nor can it be changed.

348
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:52,650
However,

349
00:22:55,010 --> 00:22:56,210
color-blind patients

350
00:22:56,730 --> 00:22:58,450
can also appreciate the splendor of art.

351
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:07,840
Everyone, please look at

352
00:23:08,040 --> 00:23:08,600
that painting.

353
00:23:10,490 --> 00:23:11,450
What can you see?

354
00:23:12,080 --> 00:23:12,840
Wheat.

355
00:23:12,970 --> 00:23:13,730
Rice.

356
00:23:14,170 --> 00:23:15,250
It's not just rice.

357
00:23:15,280 --> 00:23:17,040
What does this have to do
with the painting?

358
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:17,760
There's also wind.

359
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:22,730
There are many things in this world

360
00:23:23,730 --> 00:23:25,760
that can't only be perceived

361
00:23:25,760 --> 00:23:26,600
through color.

362
00:23:28,520 --> 00:23:30,120
Everyone, please imagine.

363
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:32,170
If you are now

364
00:23:32,170 --> 00:23:34,210
in the middle of a pitch-black night,

365
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:37,970
how can you see
the golden color of the rice paddies?

366
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:44,520
Sometimes, you don't use
your eyes to see the colors.

367
00:23:45,250 --> 00:23:46,450
We feel them.

368
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:48,760
For example, the breeze
combing through the paddies.

369
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:50,650
The fragrance of
the rice husks you smell.

370
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:52,970
They can all represent gold.

371
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,360
The sound of the wind.

372
00:24:06,840 --> 00:24:07,650
The scent of rice.

373
00:24:08,970 --> 00:24:09,730
The husk.

374
00:24:12,170 --> 00:24:13,320
That's all gold.

375
00:24:17,170 --> 00:24:18,800
We color-blind patients

376
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,520
can use other senses besides color.

377
00:24:21,210 --> 00:24:22,520
We can also use

378
00:24:23,010 --> 00:24:23,650
sound,

379
00:24:24,170 --> 00:24:24,890
touch

380
00:24:25,360 --> 00:24:26,080
and smell

381
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:27,650
to experience this world.

382
00:24:28,650 --> 00:24:29,800
You may not know this,

383
00:24:30,320 --> 00:24:31,800
but Shilun Gallery

384
00:24:31,800 --> 00:24:33,040
is holding an exhibition

385
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:35,560
for the color minority.

386
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,520
I have another piece
of good news to share.

387
00:24:44,800 --> 00:24:46,040
Mr. L

388
00:24:46,450 --> 00:24:47,320
will be participating

389
00:24:47,690 --> 00:24:48,520
the art exhibition.

