00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:50,250
Mr. L will be participating?

391
00:24:50,650 --> 00:24:52,970
Ms. Qin, please satisfy our curiosity.

392
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:55,800
What kind of person is this Mr. L?

393
00:24:57,760 --> 00:24:58,760
Mr. L...

394
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:03,120
It's better for you all to stay closer
to the artwork

395
00:25:03,410 --> 00:25:05,120
and further away from the artist.

396
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:06,760
So as to keep a sense of mystery.

397
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:08,410
A sense of mystery?

398
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:10,520
Is this a way of respecting
and protecting the artist?

399
00:25:10,520 --> 00:25:13,170
Protecting and respecting the artist.

400
00:25:13,520 --> 00:25:14,320
Yes.

401
00:25:14,360 --> 00:25:16,080
Our gallery hopes

402
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:18,410
that whether or not you can see color,

403
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:20,450
you can all experience
the splendor of art.

404
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:22,250
Even if you can't see color,

405
00:25:22,730 --> 00:25:23,680
your heart

406
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:24,410
can still feel it.

407
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:26,760
Thank you for your support.

408
00:25:26,760 --> 00:25:28,730
Welcome to our next exhibition.

409
00:25:33,520 --> 00:25:34,240
Ms, Qin,

410
