an anonymous tip-off.

411
00:25:36,010 --> 00:25:37,560
You're Su Shilun's
illegitimate daughter.

412
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:39,160
The color blindness you just admitted to

413
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:41,480
